{"tid":514588,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"香港點先可以識到一齊玩的朋友","createTime":"2017-12-30T17:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T11:55:25.000Z","uid":136686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0dff28ec71f868b79ed8d5f65c71578bb2928a3","tid":514588,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T17:11:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的,我鐘意一班人一齊玩遊戲的感覺,但我唔識埋堆<br />\n我入過幾個TCG坑,卡牌對戰的感覺尚算可以接受,只是遊戲成本高了一點<br />\n相比起打deck,我更喜歡跟牌友一起吵吵鬧鬧和玩桌遊的時光<br />\n<br />\n自從相熟的卡店轉型之後<br />\n牌友們不再組團打牌,更多是私下約戰<br />\n甚至開了一個沒邀請我的群組繼續交流<br />\n<br />\n遊戲可以換,不過我對主流TCG沒有興趣(遊戲王,WS,Magic)<br />\n再換就可能是Vangrand BS<br />\n加上TCG就是個小圈子遊戲,新玩家很難融入別人的群體當中<br />\n雖然主流遊戲隨便找間卡店都可以找到玩家對打<br />\n但是對戰只有勝和輸,總會有人感到不開心(特別係卡組強度差太遠的輾壓局)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想找桌遊,甚至TRPG團<br />\n不過不知道怎樣找<br />\n<br />\n錢可以買遊戲,但買唔到玩遊戲的過程"},{"pid":"f8cc8ab892813f11490248780d36e054fc78a4dd","tid":514588,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa3ee58f5065bcbe976c03e656e91652bd0b70f","tid":514588,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f94914df2c737d66734a63ef1ef4ed164126406","tid":514588,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aa3ee58f5065bcbe976c03e656e91652bd0b70f","tid":514588,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72096188e1fc39fb65e30f3010ef1e8f35f548e8","tid":514588,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T18:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c88c981b882405973fbdea0